languages.text: «Lo dudo. La gente como usted solo ve lo que quiere ver».

languages.text: 「それはどうかな。御身のような人は、自分が見たいものしか見ない」

languages.text: “我对此表示怀疑。像你这样的人，只能看到你们想看到的东西。”
languages.original_text: "I doubt it. People like you only ever see what they want to see."

languages.text: "Das bezweifle ich. Leute wie Ihr sehen immer nur, was sie sehen wollen."
languages.original_text: "I doubt it. People like you only ever see what they want to see."

languages.text: « J'en doute. Les gens comme vous voient uniquement ce qui les arrange. »

languages.text: "Bundan şüpheliyim. Senin gibi insanlar yalnızca anlamak istediklerini anlarlar."
